cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.DB, cs.SE, cs.PL 

This paper deals with programming with logic for sophisticated applications, which is a topic that is relevant to several sub-categories in computer science. The use of logic and constraints suggests that the paper could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). The focus on design and analysis logic suggests that it could also belong to cs.DB (Databases) or cs.SE (Software Engineering). Finally, the promotion of the use of knowledge units and the support for uncertain information suggests that it could belong to cs.PL (Programming Languages).
